                        <title xml:lang="bg">Житие на св. Василий Нови</title>
                        <author>Gregory the Monk</author>
                        <note>The copy contains the text of the Vita with disordered folia; many
                            folia appear to be missing</note>
                        <filiation type="protograph">Bulgarian</filiation>
                        <filiation type="antigraph">Bulgarian</filiation>
                        <sampleText xmlns="http://www.ilit.bas.bg/repertorium/ns/3.0" xml:lang="cu">
                            <head xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Житихе и жизнь и почести чудесъ сказанихе прѣпѡ<seg rend="sup">д</seg>обнаго о҃ца нашего Василиꙗ Новаго съписано Грихгорихемь
                                    мнихѡ<seg rend="sup">м</seg> оученико<seg rend="sup">м</seg>ь
                                егѡ. слово</head>
                            <explicit xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">и ѡбщемсе готови въ срѣтенїе Г҃ни ꙗко тому пѡ<seg rend="sup">д</seg>баеть +</explicit>
                        </sampleText>
                    </msItemStruct>
                    <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD2">
                        <locus>36v</locus>
